SUMMARY:Walking Club with Bull City Strollers
DESCRIPTION:Join us and The Bull City Strollers every Thursday for a beer and a walk! We’ll meet at the Jug at 5:30pm then go for a 30-40 minute stroll downtown with our beers in hand\, thanks to the Bullpen social district. We’ll wind up at the Jug at the end\, where pitchers of brews are always $2 off on Thursdays. Strollers\, kids\, friendly dogs\, and walkers of all speeds welcome. Stay tuned to social for updates on weather. \nView on Facebook. \nEvent runs on every Thursday starting from Jan 8\, 2026 to Jun 25\, 2026 at 5:30pm to 7:30pm.
URL:https://downtowndurham.com/event/walking-club-with-bull-city-strollers-3/2026-01-08/
LOCATION:The Glass Jug Downtown\, 545 Foster Street\, Suite 10\, Durham\, 27701
CATEGORIES:Brewery,Fitness,Health,Sports
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://downtowndurham.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Walking-Club-with-Bull-City-Strollers.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="The Glass Jug Beer Lab - Downtown Durham":MAILTO:marketing@glass-jug.com
GEO:36.0014902;-78.9018252
