SUMMARY:Silent Reading Club
DESCRIPTION:Love books but hate the “homework” of a traditional book club? Welcome to the Silent Reading Club at Glass Jug Downtown – the most social way to be antisocial! \nThe concept is simple: No assigned reading. No pressure. Simply bring a book of your choice to read in our space and grab a drink from the bar. Find a place to sit and dig in. We’ll also be hosting an optional community book recommendation share at 7pm each week. \nView on Facebook. \nThis event runs from Mar 9\, 2026 to Jun 29\, 2026 and happens every:\nMondays:6:00pm to 8:00pm
URL:https://downtowndurham.com/event/silent-reading-club-2/2026-03-16/
