SUMMARY:Mahjong Night
DESCRIPTION:Want to try a fun\, strategic game that’s been played for centuries? Join us at Glass Jug Downtown for an evening of Mahjong! \nMahjong is a mesmerizing game of skill\, strategy\, and calculation involving domino-like tiles. It’s easy to learn but offers endless depth\, making it incredibly addictive. \nMahj with Blair and Get Your Mahjong NC will teach a hands-on class to learn the basics of American Mahjong\, to build confidence\, and start playing right away. No experience needed – we’ll bring everything. \nAlready played\, but still need assistance with the game? We’ll also have guided play. \nCome from 6:30 – 8:30pm to learn to build sequences\, pairs\, pungs\, and kongs while enjoying our rotating selection of craft beer and unique cocktails. \nJoin us to learn a new skill\, challenge your brain\, and maybe even find your lucky tile! \nIntroduction Class for beginners: $40/pp\nGuided Play: $20/pp\nOpen Play: $10/pp\nSimply email getyourmahjongnc@gmail.com to reserve your space on any date and pay. \n 
URL:https://downtowndurham.com/event/mahjong-night-3/2026-03-18/
LOCATION:Glass Jug Downtown\, 545 Foster Street\, Suite 10\, Durham\, 27701
CATEGORIES:Brewery,Game Night
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://downtowndurham.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/133729.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="The Glass Jug Beer Lab - Downtown Durham":MAILTO:marketing@glass-jug.com
GEO:36.001787;-78.9017121
