SUMMARY:Music Bingo Wednesdays at Ponysaurus Brewing Co
DESCRIPTION:Did you once have an iPod with 30\,000 songs on it? Do you listen to the radio with the windows down on the reg? Did you listen to vinyl before it was cool? Then Music Bingo is for you! \nJoin Ponysaurus Brewing Co. every Wednesday at 7pm for Music Bingo with Geeks Who Drink to win beer-shaped prizes! \nHow it works: Just like regular bingo\, players will aim to win prizes by completing specific patterns on their bingo boards. Unlike regular bingo\, the boring numbers are swapped out for epic songs from all genres and eras for you to jam out to and sing along with your friends. It’s exactly the kind of laid-back fun that’s perfect for groups of any size
