SUMMARY:Baseball Photography Show - Third Friday Opening
DESCRIPTION:Get ready for baseball season with this exclusive\, first showing of Chris Ivy’s photography! Chris Ivy is the man behind the manual scoreboard for the Durham Bulls. You may have seen him on ESPN\, but now you can see his photography! Join us for a photography show highlighting behind the scenes\, chris’s points of view and fan favorites! No baseball fan will want to miss this! Chris will be on site sharing stories as well.
